  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this protocol is to define an &quot;individualized diet&quot; approach based on obesity
      related phenotypes (pathophysiology obesity classification), which would increase weight
      loss, adherence, and weight loss maintenance.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
